0stand%20again%20in%20his%20ongoing%20corruption%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20say%20to%20the%20families%20of%20the%20hostages%3A%20We%20are%20thinking%20of%20you%20and%20we%20will%20not%20give%20up%20on%20your%20loved%20ones%2C%20who%20are%20our%20loved%20ones%20as%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHostage%20families%20have%20questioned%20the%20sincerity%20of%20government%20negotiation%20efforts%2C%20and%20critics%20have%20long%20accused%20Netanyahu%20of%20stalling%20in%20truce%20talks%2C%20prolonging%20the%20war%20partly%20to%20appease%20his%20far-right%20coalition%20partners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Saturday%2C%20Hamas%2C%20Islamic%20Jihad%20and%20the%20leftist%20Popular%20Front%20for%20the%20Liberation%20of%20Palestine%20said%20progress%20had%20been%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20possibility%20of%20reaching%20an%20agreement%20(for%20a%20ceasefire%20and%20prisoner%20exchange%20deal)%20is%20closer%20than%20ever%2C%20provided%20the%20enemy%20stops%20imposing%20new%20conditions%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20groups%20said%20after%20they%20held%20talks%20in%20Cairo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20unprecedented%20Hamas%20attack%20on%20Israel%20on%20October%207%2C%202023%2C%20251%20people%20were%20abducted%2C%20of%20whom%2096%20remain%20hostages%20in%20Gaza%2C%20including%2034%20declared%20dead%20by%20the%20military.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Full%20force'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENegotiations%20have%20faced%20multiple%20challenges%20since%20a%20one-week%20truce%20in%20November%202023%2C%20with%20the%20primary%20point%20of%20contention%20being%20the%20establishment%20of%20a%20lasting%20ceasefire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20unresolved%20issue%20is%20the%20territory's%20post-war%20governance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas's%20armed%20wing%20said%20the%20fate%20of%20some%20of%20the%20captives%20depends%20on%20how%20Israeli%20forces%20carry%20out%20their%20offensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20occupation%20army%20advances%20even%20a%20few%20hundred%20metres%20more%20in%20some%20areas%20where%20they%20are%20already%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20it%20will%20decide%20the%20fate%20of%20some%20of%20the%20enemy's%20hostages%2C%26quot%3B%20Abu%20Obeida%2C%20spokesman%20for%20the%20Ezzedine%20al-Qassam%20Brigades%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20The%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20last%20week%2C%20Netanyahu%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20going%20to%20agree%20to%20end%20the%20war%20before%20we%20remove%20Hamas.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20Israel%20is%20%26quot%3Bnot%20going%20to%20leave%20them%20in%20power%20in%20Gaza%2C%2030%20miles%20from%20Tel%20Aviv.%20It's%20not%20going%20to%20happen.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Antony%20Blinken%20said%20on%20October%2023%20that%20Israel%20had%20%26quot%3Bmanaged%20to%20dismantle%20Hamas's%20military%20capacity%26quot%3B%20and%20eliminated%20its%20senior%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20those%20successes%2C%20he%20said%2C%20it%20was%20time%20to%20%26quot%3Bget%20the%20hostages%20home%20and%20bring%20the%20war%20to%20an%20end%20with%20an%20understanding%20of%20what%20will%20follow.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20Hamas%20leaders%20Israel%20killed%20was%20its%20political%20chief%20Ismail%20Haniyeh%2C%20Defence%20Minister%20Israel%20Katz%20said%20on%20Monday%2C%20in%20the%20first%20public%20acknowledgement%20that%20Israel%20was%20behind%20the%20late%20July%20death%20of%20Haniyeh%20in%20Tehran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20military%20on%20Monday%20said%20three%20soldiers%20were%20killed%20in%20northern%20Gaza%2C%20the%20focus%20for%20months%20of%20an%20offensive%20Israel%20said%20aimed%20to%20prevent%20Hamas%20from%20regrouping%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20parliament%2C%20Netanyahu%20also%20warned%20the%20Iran-backed%20Huthi%20rebels%20of%20Yemen%2C%20who%20last%20week%20fired%20two%20missiles%20at%20Israel%2C%20including%20one%20that%20injured%2016%20people%20in%20the%20commercial%20hub%20of%20Tel%20Aviv%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20instructed%20our%20forces%20to%20destroy%20the%20infrastructure%20of%20Huthis%20because%20anyone%20who%20tries%20to%20harm%20us%20will%20be%20struck%20with%20full%20force%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Beven%20if%20it%20takes%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20warplanes%20retaliated%20against%20ports%20and%20energy%20infrastructure%2C%20which%20the%20military%20said%20contributed%20to%20Huthi%20rebel%20operations%2C%20after%20a%20rebel%20missile%20badly%20damaged%20an%20Israeli%20school%20last%20week.%20The%20Huthis%20said%20the%20Israeli%20strikes%20killed%20nine%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20Israeli%20army%20said%20it%20had%20intercepted%20another%20projectile%20launched%20from%20Yemen%20before%20it%20reached%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Seize%20this%20opportunity'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Saturday%2C%20the%20United%20States%20struck%20targets%20in%20Yemen's%20rebel-held%20capital%20Sanaa%2C%20hours%20after%20the%20Huthis%20hit%20Tel%20Aviv%20with%20a%20missile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmerican%20and%20British%20forces%20have%20repeatedly%20struck%20rebel%20targets%20in%20Yemen%20this%20year%20in%20response%20to%20Huthi%20attacks%20on%20shipping%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea%20area%20vital%20to%20global%20trade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENetanyahu%20also%20stated%20that%20he%20wanted%20to%20sign%20new%20peace%20accords%20with%20Arab%20countries%2C%20similar%20to%20the%20%26quot%3BAbraham%20Accords%26quot%3B%20negotiated%20in%202020%20under%20Donald%20Trump's%20first%20US%20administration.%20Those%20agreements%20saw%20Bahrain%2C%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20and%20Morocco%20establish%20formal%20ties%20with%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BModerate%20Arab%20countries%20view%20Israel%20as%20a%20regional%20power%20and%20a%20potential%20ally.%20I%20intend%20to%20seiz