d%20her%20name%20and%20instead%20put%20forth%20the%20names%20of%20Indian%20hockey%20team%20captain%20Harmanpreet%20Singh%20for%20the%20Khel%20Ratna%20Award%2C%20Manu's%20father%20Ram%20Kishan%2C%20exclusively%20told%20Telecom%20Asia%20Sport%20that%20she%20knows%20that%20she%20deserves%20the%20award%20but%20has%20left%20it%20for%20the%20country%20to%20decide%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20I%20deserve%20it.%20Let%20the%20country%20decide%2C%26quot%3B%20Manu%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20her%20father%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20with%20Telecom%20Asia%20Sport%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20sports%20ministry%20has%20said%20that%20the%2022-year-old%20shooter%20did%20not%20apply%20for%20the%20Khel%20Ratna%2C%20her%20family%20differs%20from%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CShe%20has%20been%20applying%20for%20various%20awards%20like%20Padma%20Shri%20for%20the%20last%20four%20years.%20So%20why%20wouldn't%20she%20apply%20this%20year%3F%E2%80%9D%20questioned%20Manu's%20father%20Ram%20Kishan%20speaking%20exclusively%20with%20Telecom%20Asia%20Sport%20(www.telecomasia.net).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Ram%20Kishan%2C%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20Manu%20had%20submitted%2049%20cash%20award%20applications%20which%20she%20was%20entitled%20to%2C%20however%2C%20all%2049%20applications%20had%20been%20rejected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDespite%20such%20a%20fantastic%20performance%20if%20Manu%20is%20not%20recommended%20for%20Major%20Dhyan%20Chand%20Khel%20Ratna%2C%20then%20I%20am%20forced%20to%20believe%20that%20all%20is%20not%20well%20in%20the%20committee%2C%20or%20some%20orders%20were%20being%20followed.%20If%20we%20are%20to%20make%20India%20a%20sporting%20hub%2C%20then%20Olympic%20medallists%2C%20and%20Olympians%20in%20general%2C%20should%20be%20given%20respect%20and%20encouraged%20rather%20than%20discourage%20them%20with%20decisions%20like%20these%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ram%20Kishan%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManu%20Bhaker%20made%20history%20in%20the%20Paris%20Olympic%20Games%20by%20becoming%20the%20first%20Indian%20female%20shooter%20to%20win%20an%20Olympic%20medal%20by%20clinching%20bronze%20in%20the%20women's%2010m%20air%20pistol%20event.%20She%20followed%20that%20up%20with%20another%20bronze%20in%20the%20mixed%2010m%20air%20pistol%20team%20event%20alongside%20Sarabjot%20Singh%2C%20marking%20the%20first%20time%20any%20Indian%20has%20won%20two%20medals%20in%20a%20single%20Olympics%20since%20India's%20independence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20Bhaker%20found%20herself%20at%20the%20center%20of%20a%20controversy%20after%20posting%20on%20social%20media%2C%20questioning%20whether%20she%20deserved%20the%20Khel%20Ratna%20Award.%20The%20post%20drew%20backlash%2C%20with%20critics%20deeming%20it%20inappropriate%2C%20leading%20Bhaker%20to%20delete%20it.%20Despite%20the%20controversy%2C%20the%20absence%20of%20her%20name%20from%20the%20list%20of%20nominees%20has%20sparked%20widespread%20disappointment%20among%20her%20supporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2022-year-old%20shooter's%20performance%20in%20Paris%20was%20a%20culmination%20of%20years%20of%20determination%20and%20perseverance%2C%20especially%20after%20enduring%20the%20heartbreak%20of%20the%202020%20Tokyo%20Olympics%2C%20where%20a%20pistol%20malfunction%20derailed%20her%20campaign.%20Many%20had%20doubted%20her%20ability%20to%20bounce%20back%2C%20but%20Bhaker%20silenced%20her%20critics%20with%20a%20stunning%20comeback%20in%20Paris.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20achievements%20are%20not%20confined%20to%20the%20Olympic%20podium.%20Bhaker%20also%20added%20to%20her%20illustrious%20record%2C%20which%20already%20includes%20gold%20medals%20at%20the%20Commonwealth%20Games%20and%20the%20Asian%20Games.%20She%20claimed%20gold%20at%20the%202018%20CWG%20in%20the%20women's%2010m%20air%20pistol%20event%2C%20setting%20a%20Games%20record%2C%20and%20triumphed%20at%20the%202022%20Asian%20Games%20in%20the%20women's%2025m%20pistol%20team%20