ifts%20in%20the%20fabric%20of%20American%20society%20have%20left%20today's%20mothers%20with%20less%20support%20than%20our%20moms%20had%2C%20and%20the%2024-hour%20news%20cycle%20has%20left%20even%20more%20mothers%20fearful%20of%20leaning%20on%20their%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThankfully%2C%20that%20has%20not%20been%20our%20experience.%20While%20I%20would%20like%20to%20say%20we%20magically%20found%20our%20%26quot%3Bvillage%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20truth%20is%20that%20sometimes%20we%20have%20to%20create%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20easy%20to%20lean%20on%20neighbors%20(or%20strangers)%2C%20but%20I've%20learned%20over%20our%20decade%20in%20this%20little%20town%20that%20people%20are%20willing%20to%20look%20out%20for%20each%20other%2C%20if%20you%20open%20up%20your%20heart%20and%20let%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20we%20briefly%20lost%20our%20youngest%20child%20at%20this%20very%20same%20holiday%20event.%20While%20those%20moments%20when%20she%20wasn't%20in%20our%20eyesight%20were%20terrifying%2C%20I%20knew%20in%20my%20gut%20during%20those%20frantic%20moments%20that%20the%20adults%20in%20our%20town%20were%20looking%20out%20for%20her.%20As%20a%20neighbor%20I%20barely%20knew%20hoisted%20my%20kiddo%20above%20the%20crowd%20so%20I%20could%20find%20her%2C%20I%20teared%20up.%20This%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Floneliness-happiness-cure-coffee-shops-dense-housing-parks-walkable-neighborhoods-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecommunity%3C%2Fa%3E%20we%20are%20a%20part%20of%20looks%20out%20for%20one%20another.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2223e386ff-57fa-446f-98e5-abbb0412646a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EGiving%20our%20kids%20independence%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20kids%20are%20older%20now%3B%2013%2C%2011%20(twins)%2C%20and%206.%20We've%20given%20our%20big%20three%20more%20independence%20in%20our%20walkable%20town%20throughout%20the%20year.%20With%20kid-safe%20cell%20phones%20in%20hand%20and%20kid-friendly%20debit%20cards%20at%20their%20fingertips%2C%20we%20trusted%20our%20village%20enough%20to%20set%20them%20loose%20on%20the%20main%20street%20once%20that%20giant%20evergreen%20was%20shining%20brightly%20at%20the%20center%20of%20town.%20While%20my%2013-year-old%20and%20one%20of%20my%2011-year-old%20twins%20spent%20some%20time%20with%20us%20throughout%20the%20evening%2C%20our%20son%20Ezra%20disappeared%20into%20the%20festive%20fray%20almost%20immediately.%20I%20wasn't%20surprised.%20He's%20extroverted%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaking-dc-public-transit-alone-taught-daughter-independence-confidence-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econfident%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20has%20never%20met%20a%20festival%20he%20didn't%20love.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20many%20parents%2C%20not%20seeing%20their%20fifth%20grader%20for%20two%20hours%20on%20a%20dark%20and%20chilly%20evening%20may%20induce%20panic%2C%20but%20this%20village%20we've%20built%20and%20come%20to%20rely%20on%20gave%20us%20the%20confidence%20to%20let%20him%20test%20his%20wings.%20The%20location%20dot%20on%20his%20cell%20phone%20let%20us%20know%20he%20was%20still%20at%20the%20event%2C%20and%20a%20few%20spending%20notifications%20told%20us%20he%20was%20well%20hydrated%20and%20warm%2C%20thanks%20to%20a%20pair%20of%20LED%20gloves%20he%20purchased%20from%20a%20street%20vendor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2214353596-c619-411d-be48-4ebde6331d5b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt%20seems%20like%20our%20son%20had%20a%20great%20night%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20heard%20snippets%20about%20Ezra's%20evening%20from%20others.%20Our%20town%20librarian%20heard%20the%20DJ%20say%20his%20name%20at%20one%20point%2C%20and%20another%20friend%20let%20us%20know%20he%20helped%20pass%20out%20raffle%20baskets%20to%20the%20winners%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20evening.%20A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fraising-kids-small-town-new-hampshire-benefits-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efellow%20parent%3C%2Fa%3E%20let%20me%20know%20she%20told%20his%20friend%20group%20to%20move%20their%20horseplay%20away%20from%20some%20younger%20kids%2C%20and%20they%20readily%20complied.%20I%20thanked%20her%20for%20being%20willing%20to%20offer%20guidance%20when%20I%20didn't%20have%20eyes%20on%20him.%20%26quot%3BSure%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20want%20you%20to%20do%20the%20same%20if%20you%20saw%20my%20kid%20being%20a%20knucklehead%2C%20too.%26quot%3B%20We%20laughed%2C%20but%20I%20know%20she%20means%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20festivities%20had%20concluded%2C%20Ezra%20sent%20us%20a%20text%20asking%20if%20he%20could%20help%20the%20adults%20in%20charge%20clean%20up%20the%20event.%20We%20often%20say%20his%20big%20personality%20is%20paired%20with%20an%20even%20bigger%20heart.%20Of%20course%20we%20said%20yes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20he%20finally%20burst%20through%20our%20front%20door%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20evening%2C%20brought%20home%20by%20a%20friend's%20older%20cousin%2C%20he%20was%20cold%20and%20exhausted.%20It%20was%20after%2010%20p.m.%20and%20he%20crashed%20quickly%20into%20bed.%20I%20asked%20him%20how%20his%20night%20went%20since%20we%20had%20not%20seen%20him%20for%20over%20two%20hours.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20fun%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20I%20did%20everything%20they%20had%20to%20do.%26quot%3B%20Within%20minutes%2C%20he%20was%20out%20cold.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2223912cc0-5c15-45b7-ae57-0c2e9dfdcd37%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI'm%20glad%20we%20can%20trust%20our%20children%20%E2%80%94%20and%20our%20town%20%E2%80%94%20to%20do%20the%20right%20thing%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20days%20later%2C%20a%20local%20photographer%20shared%20a%20photo%20album%20from%20the%20festivities.%20Within%20an%20hour%20I%20had%20a%20dozen%20text%20messages%20telling%20me%20to%20take%20a%20look.%20I%20opened%20the%20link%20and%20gasped.%20There%20was%20Ezra%2C%20on%20stage%2C%20holding%20a%20tambourine.%20The%20thousand-watt%20smile%20on%20his%20face%20says%20it%20all.%20He%20had%20the%20best%20night.%20I%20have%20never%20seen%20a%20photo%20that%20better%20encapsulates%20my%20son.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EModern%20parenting%20is%20designed%20to%20provoke%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fis-surveillance-of-our-kids-making-everyone-more-anxious-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eanxiety%3C%2Fa%3E.%20From%20online%20urban%20legends%20and%20hysteria%20to%20a%20general%20lack%20of%20trust%20in%20our%20neighbors%2C%20it's%20easy%20to%20give%20into%20the%20temptation%20to%20clip%20our%20kids'%20wings%20and%20worry%20about%20how%20the%20world%20may%20harm%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20know%20the%20world%20is%20scary.%20I%20worry%20every%20day%20about%20my%20kids'%20safety.%20I%20worry%20about%20gun%20violence%2C%20online%20bullying%2C%20and%20the%20general%20divisiveness%20and%20hatred%20that%20seems%20to%20permeate%20today's%20culture.%20Rather%20than%20give%20into%20the%20temptation%20to%20shelter%20them%20at%20home%2C%20though%2C%20I've%20found%20strength%20in%20leaning%20on%20our%20community%20and%20working%20hard%20to%20foster%20independence%20in%20our%20kids.%20With%20a%20bit%20of%20help%20from%20modern%20technology%20and%20a%20whole%20lot%20of%20help%20from%20trusted%20adults%2C%20teaching%20our%20kids%20to%20navigate%20the%20world%20on%20their%20own%20feels%20like%20the%20best%20possible%20tool%20we%20can%20give%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchild-kid-run-free-holday-event-parents-not-worried-independence-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734996421000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6769d2d7a3e82c7912041788%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchild-kid-run-free-holday-event-parents-not-worried-independence-2024-12%22%2C%22summary%22