l%20other%20styles%20with%20slight%20variations%20in%20construction%20or%20style.%20We%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fblundstone-mens-dress-boot-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereviewed%20the%20Dress%20Series%20here%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20have%20had%20good%20experiences%20with%20them%2C%20but%20they're%20not%20nearly%20as%20rugged%20as%20the%20classic%20500%20and%20550%20styles%20the%20brand%20is%20known%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERegardless%20of%20which%20pair%20you%20choose%2C%20your%20Blundstones%20Chelsea%20Boots%20will%20come%20with%20the%20same%20pull%20tabs%20and%20high-traction%20TPU%20outsoles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22706f99ee-3add-472e-9a05-1be72098bf86%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Sizing%5C%22%3ESizing%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBlundstone%20boot%20sizing%20can%20be%20a%20bit%20confusing%20since%20they%20technically%20come%20in%20AUS%2FUK%20sizes.%20Most%20websites%20have%20a%20US%20conversion%20so%20you%20can%20just%20select%20your%20usual%20size%2C%20but%20this%20chart%20from%20Blundstone%20should%20help%20you%20decide%20the%20right%20AUS%2FUK%20size%20if%20there%20is%20no%20conversion%20where%20you're%20ordering%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221942%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Blundstone%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6012eeff1d2df20018b715c7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22776%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBlundstone%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20for%20some%20reason%2C%20you%20decide%20to%20go%20up%20from%20your%20true%20size%20(to%20accommodate%20heavy%20socks%20or%20maybe%20a%20wide%20foot)%2C%20it's%20best%20to%20figure%20out%20your%20US%20size%20first%2C%20and%20then%20convert%20it%20to%20the%20AUS%2FUK%20size%20to%20avoid%20confusion.%20Blundstone%20also%20offers%20half%20sizes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2283b55722-a5e3-4254-8224-1ff1edfcd853%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Shop%20all%20Blundstone%20boots%20here.%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-74554-20%26h%3D09743f64108699a38064bb9eeff3f4f9af544f752fb9b276da211f9d5588cdd9%26postID%3D61b8efdbf2a36b1ac9f49332%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fstyle%252Fblundstone-boots-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fgo.skimresources.com%253Fid%253D35871X1550380%2526xs%253D1%2526url%253Dhttps%25253A%25252F%25252Fwww.blundstone.com%25252F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShop%20all%20Blundstone%20boots%20here%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bd499bdd-27c2-430e-a989-d1522d6dae99%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Our%20personal%20reviews%20of%20Blundstone%20boots%5C%22%3EOur%20personal%20reviews%20of%20Blundstone%20boots%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAmir's%20review%20of%20the%20Blundstone%20%23585%20Men's%20Chelsea%20Boot%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20man%20wearing%20Blundstone%20boots%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6723d2f49b3250dbbceb886d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAmir%20Ismael%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c8a4d74b-8e02-46b6-96f3-a0633cb7c198%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22%C2%A0%5C%22%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ECompared%20to%20my%20other%20four%20or%20five%20other%20pairs%20of%20Chelsea%20boots%2C%20Blundstones%20are%20uniquely%20utilitarian%20and%20refreshingly%20comfortable%20to%20wear.%20While%20most%20pairs%20have%20a%20pointed%20toe%20and%20a%20sleek%2C%20tight%20upper%2C%20Blundstones%20have%20a%20wide%2C%20rounded%20toe%20and%20a%20gaitered%20upper%20that's%20wide%20enough%20to%20get%20your%20foot%20in%20without%20using%20back-breaking%20force%20and%20a%20shoehorn.%20The%20front%20and%20rear%20pull%20tabs%20make%20putting%20them%20on%20even%20easier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey're%20not%20my%20all-time%20favorite%20boots%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20style%2C%20but%20I've%20grown%20to%20appreciate%20them%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20Rustic%20colorway.%20They%20have%20a%20worn-in%20finish%2C%20which%20is%20perfect%20for%20boots%20that%20might%20get%20roughed%20up%20%E2%80%94%20if%20you%20scuff%20them%2C%20it'll%20blend%20right%20into%20the%20natural%20look.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20like%20that%20I%20can%20dress%20them%20up%20with%20jeans%20and%20a%20nice%20sweater%20for%20a%20comfortable%20look%2C%20but%20still%20wear%20them%20with%20all%20of%20my%20warmest%20layers%20and%20take%20on%20a%20snowstorm.%20As%20seen%20in%20the%20pictures%20above%2C%20I%20wouldn't%20hesitate%20to%20wear%20them%20in%20the%20snow.%20The%20outsoles%20have%20more%20than%20enough%20grip%20to%20confidently%20traverse%20wet%2C%20slippery%2C%20or%20slushy%20situations%20in%20the%20winter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESizing%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EBlundstones%20are%20based%20on%20AUS%2FUK%20sizes%2C%20which%20is%20a%20full%20size%20smaller%20than%20US%20sizes.%20I'm%20a%20true%20US%20size%208%2C%20so%20I%20went%20with%20the%20AUS%2FUK%20size%207%20and%20they%20fit%20perfectly.%C2%A0%20%E2%80%94%3Cstrong%3EAmir%20Ismael%2C%20style%20editor%2C%20Reviews%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESally's%20review%20of%20Blundstone%20%23566%20Women's%20Thermal%20Chelsea%20Boots%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Blundstone%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5ff76401d184b30018aad997%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222250%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESally%20Kaplan%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20worn%20my%20Blundstone%20Thermal%20boots%20through%20two%20winter%20seasons%20in%20NYC%2C%20and%20I%20love%20them%20more%20every%20time%20I%20put%20them%20on.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20pair%20is%20fully%20waterproof%20with%20warm%20Thinsulate%20insulation%20and%20has%20a%20shearling%20insole%20for%20extra%20warmth.%20I've%20stood%20in%20icy%20puddles%2C%20walked%20through%20muddy%20parks%2C%20and%20worn%20them%20on%20snowy%20walks%20without%20ever%20staining%20the%20leather%20or%20breaching%20the%20leak-proof%20seal.%20My%20feet%20are%20always%20warm%2C%20and%20my%20arches%20feel%20supported%20by%20the%20thick%2C%20cushy%20soles.%20The%20elastic%20band%20at%20the%20side%20also%20keeps%20the%20shoe%20from%20digging%20into%20my%20calf.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20one%20downside%20of%20the%20Thermal%20pair%20is%20that%20they%20are%20really%20meant%20for%20cold%20weather%2C%20so%20they%20can%20be%20too%20warm%20to%20wear%20in%20more%20moderate%20temps%20or%20over%20the%20summer.%20I%20usually%20start%20wearing%20them%20in%20the%20fall%20and%20put%20them%20away%20in%20the%20spring%2C%20swapping%20them%20out%20for%20more%20lightweight%20summer%20Chelsea%20boots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESizing%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EMy%20one%20pet%20peeve%20with%20the%20boots%20is%20that%20the%20heel%20tends%20to%20pull%20down%20my%20socks%2C%20but%20I%20think%20this%20is%20because%20I%20opted%20to%20size%20down%20in%20my%20pair.%20I'm%20usually%20between%20a%207.5%20and%20an%208%20depending%20on%20the%20brand%2C%20and%20since%20Blundstones%20are%20said%20to%20run%20a%20smidge%20big%2C%20I%20opted%20for%20the%207.5.%20I%20probably%20would%20have%20been%20able%20to%20avoid%20the%20sock%20issue%20with%20a%20size%208%2C%20but%20the%207.5%20still%20fits%20my%20feet%20well%20enough%20that%20I%20don't%20feel%20like%20I'm%20squishing%20into%20the%20shoe.%20Overall%2C%20I%20say%20go%20true-to-size%20or%20if%20you're%20in%20between%20sizes%2C%20go%20with%20the%20larger%20one.%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cstrong%3ESally%20Kaplan%2C%20executive%20editor%2C%20Reviews%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOwen's%20review%20of%20the%20Blundstone%20%231477%20Men's%20Thermal%20Chelsea%20Boot%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Blundstone%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5ff76899d184b30018aad9ad%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222250%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EOwen%20Burke%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c83474cc-b825-4a42-8f95-22598946aa40%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22%C2%A0%5C%22%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20not%20the%20most%20fashionable%20reporter%20here%20%E2%80%94%20far%20from%20it%20%E2%80%94%20but%20when%20I%20first%20got%20a%20pair%20of%20Blundstone%20boots%2C%20while%20I%20appreciated%20them%20for%20their%20rough-and-ready%20design%2C%20I%20wasn't%20a%20huge%20fan%20of%20the%20aesthetic.%20What's%20with%20the%20two%20oversized%20tags%3F%20Is%20this%20a%20Chelsea%20boot%20for%20shepherds%3F%20For%20old%20folks%3F%20I%20couldn't%20quite%20place%20the%20style.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20I%20slipped%20them%20on%20and%20thought%2C%20these%20are%20Ugg%20boots%20masquerading%20as%20something%20a%20little%20less%20frumpy%2C%20a%20little%20less%20embarrassing%20(for%20me).%20The%20shearling%20lining%20on%20the%20insole%20offers%20the%20same%20effect%20of%20walking%20on%20a%20pillow%20or%20a%20cloud%2C%20but%20this%20was%20a%20pair%20of%20boots%20I%20could%20stand%20to%20be%20caught%20dead%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20these%20are%20about%20the%20only%20boots%20that%20grace%20my%20feet%2C%20save%20for%20particularly%20wet%20excursions%20when%20the%20Muck%20Boots%20come%20out.%20I%20can%20pull%20these%20off%20in%20the%20office%20(when%20I'm%20there)%2C%20and%20they%20can%20be%20reasonably%20dressed%20up%20or%20down%20depending%20on%20where%20I%20am%20and%20how%20out-of-place%20I%20feel.%20And%20guess%20what%3F%20Those%20two%20oversized%20loops%20that%20I%20once%20found%20to%20be%20flagrantly%20disagreeable%20have%20earned%20their%20place.%20Popping%20these%20puppies%20on%20and%20off%20is%20a%20breeze%2C%20and%20I've%20grown%20to%20find%20their%20flair%20kind%20of%20fun%20after%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20well%20into%20my%20second%20season%20of%20almost%20exclusively%20wearing%20Blundstone%20boots%20through%20fall%2C%20winter%2C%20and%20spring%2C%20often%20trudging%20upwards%20of%20five%20miles%20through%20horrendous%20city%20sludge%20and%20worse%2C%20and%20they%20continue%20to%20show%20no%20sign%20of%20letting%20up%3A%20neither%20a%20single%20stitch%20loose%20nor%20a%20leak%20sprung.%20I've%20taken%20boots%20twice%20their%20price%20into%20their%20final%20throes%20by%20this%20point%2C%20but%20I'll%20make%20no%20mistakes%20going%20forward.%20The%20next%20pair%20of%20boots%20I%20buy%2C%20whenever%20this%20one%20gives%20up%20its%20ghost%2C%20is%20going%20to%20be%20Blundstone%2C%20and%20I%20might%20just%20go%20ahead%20and%20put%20my%20money%20on%20the%20pair%20after%20that%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESizing%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20went%20with%20a%20size%2010%20AU%2FUK%20because%20I'm%20usually%20a%20US%20size%2011.%20They%20fit%20perfectly.%20The%20toe%20box%20is%20large%20and%20I'm%20able%20to%20move%20my%20toes%20around%20(crucial%20for%20mobility%2C%20but%20also%20for%20keeping%20your%20toes%20moving%20and%20warm%20when%20you're%20standing%20out%20in%20the%20cold%20for%20long%20periods%20of%20time).%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cstrong%3EOwen%20Burke%2C%20former%20reporter%2C%20Reviews%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMaria's%20review%20of%20the%20Blundstone%20%231351%20Women's%20Chelsea%20Boot%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Blundstone%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5ff789d4d184b30018aadaa4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222250%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EMaria%20Del%20Russo%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f23920b4-2e90-48b1-bddc-f800ea5d566d%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22%C2%A0%5C%22%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20a%20Doc%20Marten%20person%20for%20as%20long%20as%20I%20can%20remember%2C%20but%20I%20never%20really%20loved%20the%20look%20of%20the%20brand's%20Chelsea%20boots.%20So%20when%20my%20colleague%20Sally%20Kaplan%20told%20me%20about%20these%20Blundstones%2C%20I%20was%20almost%20immediately%20smitten.%20I%20got%20them%20in%20rustic%20brown%2C%20and%20I%20haven't%20really%20taken%20them%20off%20since.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20feet%20that%20are%20super%20wide%20up%20top%2C%20but%20that%20taper%20near%20the%20ankles%2C%20so%20pull-on%20shoes%20are%20typically%20tough%20for%20me%20to%20wear%20comfortably.%20The%20Blundstone's%20double%20pull%20tabs%20and%20elastic%20side%20make%20it%20easy%20for%20me%20to%20slide%20them%20on%20and%20off%2C%20although%20I%20will%20admit%20it%20took%20a%20few%20tries%20to%20break%20them%20in.%20The%20brogue%20detailing%20gives%20these%20boots%20flare%2C%20but%20the%20water-resistant%20leather%20and%20lug%20soles%20mean%20they%20can%20hang%20through%20a%20walk%20through%20the%20mud.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20also%20been%20shocked%20at%20how%20comfortable%20these%20boots%20are%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20cushioned%20midsole.%20I've%20worn%20them%20all%20day%20without%20foot%20pain.%20And%20even%20though%20they%C2%A0%3Cem%3Eact%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0like%20technical%20boots%2C%20they%20don't%20look%20like%20them.%20I've%20worn%20them%20to%20dinner%20with%20friends%20with%20straight-leg%20jeans%20and%20with%20leggings%20and%20thick%20socks%20and%20they've%20looked%20slick%20with%20either%20outfit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESizing%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20If%20your%20feet%20are%20on%20the%20wider%20side%20like%20mine%2C%20you%20might%20want%20to%20go%20a%20half-size%20up%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20what%20I%20did%2C%20and%20these%20boots%20fit%20comfortably.%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cstrong%3EMaria%20Del%20Russo%2C%20former%20style%20editor%2C%20Reviews%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EShalom's%20review%20of%20the%20Blundstone%20%231941%20Men's%20Chelsea%20Boot%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Blundstone%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5ff767836d61c10019cce378%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221125%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EShalom%20Goodman%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2256d952c8-d2f3-46f9-8263-69aaef9b8d5e%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22%C2%A0%5C%22%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EEver%20since%20I%20got%20my%20Chelsea%20Boot%20Classic%20Blundstones%20a%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20I've%20worn%20them%20pretty%20much%20nonstop%20for%20the%20entire%20fall%20and%20winter%20seasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20man%20of%20habit%2C%20I%20wear%20my%20classic%20Birkenstock%20Boston%20slip-on%20shoe%20up%20until%20a%20friend%20will%20inevitably%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BBro%2C%20it's%2035%20degrees%20out%2C%20put%20on%20real%20shoes.%26quot%3B%20At%20that%20point%2C%20I%20put%20on%20my%20Blundstones.%20The%20comfort%2C%20the%20reliability%2C%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20they%20go%20with%20most%20of%20my%20wardrobe%20really%20does%20it%20for%20me.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20highly%20recommend%20these%20to%20anyone%20who%20just%20wants%20a%20versatile%2C%20laid-back%2C%20fun%20boot%20that%20works%20for%20all%20occasions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESizing%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20went%20with%20my%20true%20US%20size%2013%2C%20which%20converts%20to%20an%20AUS%20size%2012.%20The%20fit%20is%20just%20right%20for%20a%20person%20with%20average%20shaped%20feet%2C%20with%20plenty%20of%20wiggle%20room%2C%20but%20snug%20enough%20to%20feel%20secure.%C2%A0%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cstrong%3EShalom%20Goodman%2C%20former%20SEO%20strategist%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ECons%20to%20consider%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Blundstone%20Boots%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6000b6a8b80507001899536c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESally%20Kaplan%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20aren't%20many%20cons%20to%20consider%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20Blundstones%2C%20but%20the%20tricky%20way%20styles%20are%20labeled%20is%20probably%20our%20biggest%20complaint.%20The%20differences%20in%20models%20and%20series%20aren't%20always%20clearly%20labeled%20or%20easy%20to%20figure%20out.%20That%20said%2C%20we've%20never%20met%20a%20pair%20we%20didn't%20like%2C%20even%20if%20we%20couldn't%20always%20tell%20the%20differences%20between%20similar%20styles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20bottom%20line%3Cp%3EPriced%20between%20%24200-%24230%2C%20Blundstone%20boots%20are%20a%20solid%20value.%20We've%20tried%20more%20expensive%20boots%20that%20are%20less%20comfortable%20and%20less%20dependable%20in%20harsh%20weather.%20Blundstone%20boots%20work%20for%20nearly%20every%20season%20where%20boots%20are%20appropriate%2C%20and%20the%20classic%20Chelsea%20silhouette%20will%20never%20go%20out%20of%20style.%20Overall%2C%20we%20know%20we're%20getting%20a%20good%20value%20when%20we%20buy%20a%20pair%20of%20these%20boots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fblundstone-boots-review%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734988636000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5ff74087d184b30018aad8b9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fblundstone-boots-review%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Several%20people%20on%20Business%20Insider's%20Reviews%20team%20swear%20by%20their%20Blundstone%20boots%2C%20so%20I%20asked%20them%20to%20share%20how%20their%20pairs%20fit%2C%20feel%2C%20and%20perform.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22aismael%40businessinsider.com%20(Amir%20Ismael)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fblundstone-boots-review%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%