5_625x300_12_November_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20a%20report%20in%20the%20Hong%20Kong-based%20South%20China%20Morning%20Post%2C%20which%20further%20quotes%20the%20Pakistani%20media%2C%20China%20will%20deliver%20all%2040%20stealth%20fighter%20jest%20in%20less%20than%20two%20years.%20China's%20entire%20defence%20industry%20is%20already%20set%20up%20for%20mass%20production%20as%20it%20does%20not%20depend%20on%20any%20other%20country%20for%20any%20part%20of%20the%20aircraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20also%20states%20that%20Pakistan's%20Air%20Force%20has%20already%20approved%20the%20purchase%20of%20these%20jets.%20Though%20there%20is%20no%20confirmation%20from%20Beijing%2C%20should%20such%20a%20deal%20materialise%2C%20it%20will%20provide%20Pakistan%20a%20massive%20boost%20to%20its%20air%20defence%20and%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20tilt%20the%20regional%20dynamic%20as%20Islamabad%20will%20acquire%20stealth%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWHAT%20IS%20KNOWN%20ABOUT%20THE%20CHINESE%20J-35A%20STEALTH%20AIRCRAFT%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Shenyang%20J-35A%20stealth%20fighter%20is%20a%20twin-engine%2C%20single-seater%2C%20supersonic%2C%20air-superiority%2C%20multi-role%20fighter%20jet%20that%20can%20carry%20out%20missions%20on%20land%20and%20at%20sea.%20The%20J-35A%20is%20the%20second%20fifth-generation%20stealth%20fighter%20China%20has%20developed%20after%20the%20J-20.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20J-35A's%20design%20is%20similar%20to%20the%20US%20Lockheed%20Martin%20F-35%2C%20the%20only%20difference%20is%20that%20the%20former%20is%20twin-engine%20and%20the%20latter%20has%20a%20single%20engine.%20China%20is%20known%20for%20copying%20the%20design%20of%20several%20US%20aircraft%20-%20The%20J-20%20and%20the%20US%20F-22%20Raptor%20are%20very%20similar%20in%20design%20except%20for%20canards%20that%20are%20present%20in%20J-20.%20The%20Chengdu%20J-10%2C%20also%20known%20as%20the%20%26quot%3BVigorous%20Dragon%26quot%3B%2C%20is%20yet%20another%20Chinese%20aircraft%20which%20seems%20to%20be%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20US%20F-16%20fighter%20jet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2F9s4re0d_f22-j20_625x300_12_November_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Csmall%3E%3Cem%3EUS%20F-22%20Raptor%20(Left)%2C%20China%20J-20%20(Right)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsmall%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20by%20the%20Global%20Times%2C%20the%20mouthpiece%20of%20the%20Chinese%20Communist%20Party%2C%20%26quot%3BJ-35A%20functions%20within%20both%20stealth%20and%20counter-stealth%20combat%20frameworks.%20Its%20mission%20focuses%20on%20gaining%20and%20maintaining%20air%20superiority%2C%20eliminating%20hostile%20fourth%2Ffifth%20generation%20fighter%20jets%20and%20ground%2Fsurface%20air%20defence%20forces%2C%20as%20well%20as%20intercepting%20aerial%20hostile%20targets%20including%20fighters%2C%20bombers%20and%20cruise%20missiles.%26quot%3B%20The%20article%20was%20published%20the%20day%20China%20unveiled%20the%20jet%20for%20the%20first%20time%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20plans%20to%20induct%20the%20aircraft%20into%20the%20Air%20Force%20and%20the%20Navy%2C%20exactly%20the%20way%20the%20F-35%20is%20used%20by%20the%20United%20States%2C%20having%20three%20variants%20-%20The%20F-35A%20for%20the%20Air%20Force%2C%20F-35B%20for%20the%20Marine%20Corps%20and%20F-35C%20for%20the%20US%20Navy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fi1j8rtds_f35-fighter-jet-f-35-lightning-ii-jet_625x300_01_October_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Csmall%3E%3Cem%3EUS%20F-35%20Lighting%20carrying%20out%20formation%20flying%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsmall%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EPAKISTAN'S%20ECONOMIC%20CRISIS%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20a%20severe%20economic%20crisis%20in%20the%20country%2C%20Pakistan%2C%20which%20is%20surviving%20on%20bailout%20packages%20by%20the%20IMF%20and%20World%20Bank%2C%20is%20reportedly%20going%20ahead%20with%20the%20deal.%20It%20is%20not%20clear%20though%2C%20how%20such%20a%20massive%20deal%20will%20get%20financed.%20According%20to%20defence%20experts%2C%20it%20won't%20come%20as%20a%20surprise%20should%20China%20decide%20to%20extend%20another%20loan%20which%20Pakistan%20won't%20able%20able%20to%20pay%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%20has%20already%20accumulated%20so%20much%20debt%20from%20Beijing%20that%20it%20is%20not%20financially%20possible%20for%20Islamabad%20to%20pay%20it%20back.%20Many%20experts%20believe%20that%20at%20some%20point%20Pakistan%20will%20have%20to%20sell%20national%20assets%20and%20maybe%20even%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20to%20be%20able%20to%20settle%20the%20debt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20buzz%20is%20ripe%20in%20Islamabad%2C%20Beijing%20has%20not%20confirmed%20the%20sale%20of%20its%20stealth%20fighter%20jet%20in%20any%20official%20communication.%20Neither%20has%20it%20mentioned%20it%20in%20the%20passing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20J-35A%20stealth%20fighter%20was%20first%20displayed%20publicly%20by%20China%20at%20the%20annual%20air%20show%20at%20Zhuhai%20city%20in%20November%2C%20top%20Pakistan%20Air%20Force%20officials%20visited%20the%20exhibition%20and%20were%20seen%20holding%20talks%20with%20senior%20Chinese%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20the%20report%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22No%20follow%2C%20no%20index%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fchina%2Fmilitary%2Farticle%2F3291826%2Fpakistans-reported-j-35-deal-shows-chinese-stealth-fighter-ready-global-market-analysts%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESouth%20China%20Morning%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Pakistan%20Air%20Force%20Chief%20Air%20Marshal%20Zaheer%20Ahmed%20Baber%20Sidhu%20said%20in%20January%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20foundation%20for%20acquiring%20the%20J-31%20stealth%20fighter%20aircraft%20has%20already%20been%20laid.%26quot%3B%20The%20J-31%20is%20considered%20the%20land%20version%20of%20the%20J-35A%2C%20which%20was%20originally%20believed%20to%20be%20a%20naval%20aircraft%2C%20but%20was%20later%20launched%20as%20a%20multi-role%20fighter%20jet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20Pakistan's%20inability%20to%20pay%20back%2C%20China%20has%20over%20time%20steadily%20increased%20its%20military%20supply%20to%20Islamabad%20by%20modernising%20all%20three%20branches%20of%20the%20Pakistani%20military%2C%20spending%20several%20billion%20dollars%20in%20the%20country's%20defence%20expenditure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20has%20also%20jointly%20developed%20and%20operates%20the%20J-17%20Thunder%20fighter%20jet%20with%20Pakistan.%20For%20its%20navy%2C%20China%20has%20already%20delivered%20four%20advanced%20naval%20frigates%20to%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMEETING%20BETWEEN%20CHINA%20AND%20PAKISTAN%20OVER%20THE%20REPORTED%20DEAL%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETop%20Chinese%20Army%20General%20Zhang%20Youxia%20visited%20Pakistan%20in%20November%20shortly%20after%20unveiling%20the%20J-35A%20stealth%20aircraft%2C%20during%20which%20he%20held%20closed-door%20talks%20with%20Pakistan's%20Army%20chief%20Gen%20Asim%20Munir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGen%20Zhang%20is%20the%20Vice-Chairman%20of%20the%20Central%20Military%20Comm%C2%ADission%20or%20CMC%2C%20which%20is%20the%20overall%20command%20of%20the%20Chinese%20military.%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20heads%20the%20commission%2C%20and%20is%20briefed%20directly%20about%20such%20meetings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20meeting%2C%20the%20Inter-Services%20Public%20Relations%20or%20ISPR%2C%20the%20media%20wing%20of%20the%20Pakistani%20armed%20forces%20issued%20a%20statement%20which%20said%20the%20meeting%20between%20the%20two%20focused%20on%20%26quot%3Bmatters%20of%20mutual%20interest%2C%20regional%20security%20dynamics%2C%20measures%20for%20regional%20stability%2C%20and%20enhancing%20bilateral%20defence%20cooperation%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EPAKISTAN'S%20SOVEREIGNTY%20UNDER%20THREAT%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Pakistani%20media%2C%20during%20these%20recent%20meetings%2C%20China%20has%20been%20increasing%20pressure%20on%20Islamabad%20to%20allow%20Beijing's%20security%20firms%20and%20agencies%20to%20send%20boots%20on%20ground%20in%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20reportedly%20intends%20on%20sending%20an%20initial%20lot%20of%20more%20than%2020%2C000%20soldiers%20and%20security%20personnel%20to%20be%20deployed%20at%20various%20locations%20along%20the%20so-called%20China-Pakistan%20Economic%20Corridor%20or%20CPEC%2C%20which%20it%20is%20constructing%20through%20Pakistan-occupied%20Kashmir%20(PoK)%20and%20in%20the%20turbulent%20region%20of%20Balochistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20Pakistani%20media%20reports%2C%20Islamabad%20says%20it%20has%20deployed%20over%2030%2C000%20dedicated%20military%20and%20para-military%20personnel%20just%20to%20protect%20Chinese%20workers%20working%20on%20project%20pertaining%20to%20the%20so-called%20CPEC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reports%20further%20state%20that%20so%20far%2C%20Pakistan%20has%20somehow%20been%20resisting%20Beijing's%20pressure%20to%20deploy%20Chinese%20troops%20across%20Pakistan%20over%20sovereignty%20concerns.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734981600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fbgqs8ac_china-j35a-stealth-fighter-jet-china-j-35-getty_625x300_23_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpakistan-may-get-40-5th-gen-stealth-fighter-jets-from-china-within-2-years-report-7317114%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20game-changing%20