oup%20chief%20executive%20for%20consulting%20at%20Accenture%2C%20said%20at%20one%20Workforce%20Innovation%20roundtable.%20%26quot%3BVery%20few%20have%20a%20coherent%20business%20case%20and%20a%20true%20reinvention%20and%20transformation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHow%20do%20companies%20move%20forward%20as%20the%20novelty%20of%20AI%20wears%20off%3F%20Business%20Insider's%20Julia%20Hood%20asked%20members%20of%20the%20Workforce%20Innovation%20board%20how%20they%20transitioned%20their%20AI%20pilots%20into%20real-world%20use%20cases.%20Board%20members%20shared%20five%20major%20ways%20their%20companies%20were%20moving%20AI%20from%20theory%20to%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBefore%20we%20go%20and%20tell%20our%20clients%20to%20embark%20on%20AI%20fully%2C%20we%20want%20to%20be%20an%20AI-first%20organization%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Anant%20Adya%2C%20an%20executive%20vice%20president%2C%20service-offering%20head%2C%20and%20head%20of%20Americas%20delivery%20at%20Infosys.%20%26quot%3BWe%20want%20to%20show%20our%20clients%20we%20are%20using%20AI%2C%20whether%20it%20is%20in%20HR%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20driving%20better%20employee%20experience%20or%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20recruitment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMembers%20also%20highlighted%20employee%20training%20and%20peer-to-peer%20learning%20opportunities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20roundtable%20participants%20were%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAnant%20Adya%2C%20an%20executive%20vice%20president%2C%20service-offering%20head%2C%20and%20head%20of%20Americas%20Delivery%20at%20Infosys.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ELucrecia%20Borgonovo%2C%20a%20chief%20talent%20and%20organizational-effectiveness%20officer%20at%20Mastercard.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENeil%20Murray%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Work%20Dynamics%20at%20JLL.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EJustina%20Nixon-Saintil%2C%20a%20vice%20president%20and%20chief%20impact%20officer%20at%20IBM.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMarjorie%20Powell%2C%20a%20chief%20HR%20officer%20and%20senior%20vice%20president%20at%20AARP.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22919d501d-07ec-4e5e-b493-342bef0e1945%5C%22%3EIdentify%20early%20adopters%2C%20like%20human%20resources%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENixon-Saintil%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EBecause%20we%20provide%20these%20platforms%20and%20solutions%20to%20clients%2C%20we%20are%20usually%20client%20zero.%20We%20implemented%20AI%20across%20our%20business%20and%20multiple%20functions%2C%20and%20one%20of%20the%20first%20things%20we%20did%20was%20our%20AskHR%20product%2C%20which%20I%20think%20answered%20over%2094%25%20of%20questions%20employees%20had.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHR%20employees%20now%20spend%20time%20doing%20higher-order%20work%20and%20partnerships%20with%20business%20units%20instead%20of%20answering%20basic%20questions%20that%20a%20virtual%20assistant%20can%20answer.%20I%20think%20that's%20when%20you%20start%20seeing%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20benefits%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBorgonovo%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EHR%20has%20been%20leading%20the%20way%20in%20terms%20of%20embedding%20AI%20to%20enhance%20the%20employee%20experience%20end%20to%20end%2C%20right%20before%20you%20hire%20somebody%20all%20the%20way%20to%20after%20they%20leave%20the%20organization.%20There%20are%20tons%20of%20opportunities%20to%20improve%20performance%20and%20productivity%20and%20provide%20greater%20personalization.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fdec2d3f-8653-4d98-97e5-a6ceccb878cf%5C%22%3EInvest%20in%20ongoing%20training%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAdya%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThere%20are%20certain%20AI%20certifications%20and%20courses%20that%20everybody%20has%20to%20take%20to%20be%20knowledgeable%20about%20AI.%20So%20we%20are%20driving%20education%20in%20terms%20of%20what%20is%20the%20impact%20of%20AI%2C%20what%20is%20gen%20AI%2C%20what%20are%20LLMs%2C%20and%20how%20you%20look%20at%20use%20cases.%20And%20certainly%20educating%20everybody%20that%20it's%20not%20about%20job%20losses%20but%20about%20amplifying%20your%20potential%20to%20do%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPowell%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWe%20have%20hands-on%20skill%20building.%20This%20past%20year%20we%20posted%20over%2020%20AI%20workshops%20helping%20teams%20integrate%20AI%20into%20their%20work.%20We%20really%20encourage%20our%20staff%20to%20participate.%20We%20have%20a%20product%20we're%20using%20behind%20our%20firewall%2C%20so%20they%20can%20engage%20and%20play%20with%20it.%20We're%20just%20telling%20them%20go%20ahead%20and%20try%20to%20break%20it%2C%20so%20they%20can%20give%20us%20feedback%20on%20what's%20working.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20a%20team%20of%20people%20who%20said%20we%20want%20to%20see%20how%20you%20could%20use%20AI%20with%20PowerPoint%20or%20Excel.%20And%20they're%20finding%2C%20well%2C%20it's%20not%20so%20good%20in%20those%20things.%20But%20as%20it%20continues%20to%20grow%2C%20they'll%20be%20ready%20for%20that%2C%20and%20they'll%20know%20what%20it%20was%20able%20to%20do%20and%20what%20it%20wasn't.%20I%20think%20it's%20just%20making%20it%20fun%2C%20and%20that%20way%20it's%20not%20so%20scary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMurray%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EOur%20internal%20large%20language%20model%20is%20now%20a%20widget%20on%20everybody's%20dashboard%20that%20is%20accessible%20on%20your%20landing%20page.%20Training%20is%20super%20important%20here%20to%20make%20people%20comfortable%20with%20it.%20Even%20if%20it's%20just%20an%20online%20module%2C%20you%20have%20to%20get%20people%20comfortable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENixon-Saintil%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWe've%20also%20done%20companywide%20upskilling.%20We%20had%20two%20Watsonx%20challenges.%20Watsonx%20is%20our%20AI%20data%20platform.%20This%20is%20one%20of%20the%20ways%20we've%20upskilled%20a%20majority%20of%20the%20organization.%20The%20outcome%20of%20that%20is%20there%20are%20some%20great%20ideas%20that%20employees%20actually%20ideated%2C%20and%20they're%20now%20implementing%20those%20ideas%20and%20solutions%20in%20different%20functions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBorgonovo%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EEmployees%20want%20to%20use%20AI%2C%20and%20I%20think%20they're%20eager%20to%20learn%20how%20to%20use%20AI%20to%20augment%20their%20jobs.%20For%20that%2C%20we%20built%20a%20three-tiered%20learning%20approach.%20One%20is%20democratizing%20access%20for%20everybody%20and%20building%20general%20knowledge%20of%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20tier%20is%20much%20more%20role-specific.%20How%20do%20we%20drive%20new%20ways%20of%20working%20by%20having%20people%20in%20different%20roles%20embrace%20AI%20tools%3F%20Software%20engineering%2C%20consulting%2C%20sales%20%E2%80%94%20you%20name%20it.%20And%20then%20something%20we%20definitely%20want%20to%20build%20for%20the%20future%20is%20thinking%20proactively%20about%20how%20you%20re-skill%20people%20whose%20roles%20may%20be%20impacted%20by%20AI%20so%20they%20can%20become%20more%20comfortable%20doing%20high-level%20tasks%20or%20can%20shift%20to%20a%20different%20type%20of%20role%20that%20is%20emerging%20within%20the%20organization.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20piece%20is%20where%20we're%20seeing%20the%20greatest%20demand%20internally%2C%20which%20is%20for%20knowledge%20management.%20It's%20gathering%20information%20from%20a%20lot%20of%20different%20sources%20in%20a%20very%20easy%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20job%20family%20that%20is%20very%20eager%20to%20get%20their%20hands%20on%20new%20AI%20technology%20is%20software%20engineering.%20We%20have%20taken%20a%20very%20measured%20approach%20in%20deploying%20coding%20assistants%20within%20the%20software-engineering%20community.%20This%20year%20we%20did%20a%20pilot%20with%20a%20subset%20of%20them%20using%20coding%20assistants.%20The%20idea%20is%20to%20just%20learn%20and%2C%20based%20on%20our%20learning%2C%20scale%20more%20broadly%20across%20our%20software-engineering%20community%20in%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20really%20interesting%20learnings%20from%20this%20pilot%20was%20that%20the%20software%20engineers%20who%20were%20using%20the%20coding%20assistants%20probably%20the%20best%20were%20people%20who%20had%20received%20training.%20What%20we're%20learning%20is%20that%20before%20you%20start%20rolling%20out%20all%20of%20these%20technologies%20or%20AI-specific%20platforms%20for%20different%20job%20families%2C%20you%20have%20got%20to%20be%20really%20intentional%20about%20incorporating%20prompt%20training.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cf24125b-e38e-4f1e-9bcd-b1f12ce8b5ab%5C%22%3EUnlock%20peer-to-peer%20learning%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPowell%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWe%20have%20idea%20pitch%20competitions%20and%20a%20year-round%20idea%20pipeline%20program%20where%20people%20can%20put%20in%20ideas%20on%20how%20to%20use%20AI%20and%20share%20what%20they've%20learned.%20It%20sparks%20a%20lot%20of%20peer%20learning%20and%20creativity%20on%20our%20digital-first%20capabilities%20to%20help%20us%20with%20our%20digital%20transformation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20we%20collaborate%20through%20community.%20We%20have%20a%20generative-AI%20community%20of%20practice.%20This%20is%20somewhat%20like%20how%20companies%20have%20employee%20resource%20groups%3B%20we%20have%20communities%20of%20practice%20as%20well.%20They%20give%20employees%20a%20space%20to%20share%20their%20techniques%20and%20learn%20from%20each%20other%20and%20stay%20ahead%20of%20evolving%20trends.%20They%20meet%20monthly%2C%20they%20have%20an%20executive%20sponsor%2C%20and%20they%20have%20all%20kinds%20of%20activities%20and%20learning%20opportunities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMurray%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAs%20we%20monitored%20AI%20use%20and%20what%20sort%20of%20questions%20were%20being%20asked%2C%20we%20identified%20super%20users%20across%20all%20departments%20%E2%80%94%20so%20the%20people%20who%20were%20capable%20of%20developing%20the%20most%20evolved%20prompts.%20I%20suppose%20those%20prompts%20are%20now%20appearing%20in%20pull-down%20menus%20to%20help%20people%20who%20maybe%20aren't%20as%20advanced%20in%20their%20use%20of%20it%2C%20because%20prompting%20is%20a%20really%20important%20part%20of%20this.%20And%20so%20the%20super%20users%20are%20driving%20everybody%20else%20to%20show%20them%20what's%20possible%20across%20the%20organization.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226444cf11-181d-4861-91c7-6457200455f8%5C%22%3EFind%20customer%20pain%20points%20to%20solve%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBorgonovo%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EOne%20of%20the%20use%20cases%20that%20drives%20not%20only%20knowledge%20management%20but%20also%20efficiencies%20is%20around%20customer%20support.%20Customer%20support%20is%20probably%20one%20of%20the%20areas%20that%20has%20been%20leading%20the%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20a%20customer%20onboarding%20process%20that%20can%20be%20very%20lengthy%2C%20very%20technical%2C%20involving%20hundreds%20of%20pages%20of%20documentation%20and%20reference%20materials.%20It%20was%20our%20first%20use%20case%20for%20a%20chat-based%20assistant%20that%20we%20processed%20in%20terms%20of%20streamlining%20and%20creating%20greater%20efficiency%20and%20a%20much%20better%20customer%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229fd85d5a-e451-4b55-b2aa-0df09d6e491f%5C%22%3EReinforce%20responsible%20leadership%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPowell%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWe%20want%20our%20leaders%2C%20people%20leaders%20particularly%2C%20to%20guide%20employees%20to%20use%20AI%20effectively%20and%20responsibly.%20We%20want%20to%20make%20sure%20they're%20emphasizing%20privacy%2C%20policy%2C%20and%20efficiency.%20So%20we%20encourage%20managers%20to%20point%20the%20staff%20toward%20training%20that%20we%20offer%2C%20and%20we%20offer%20quite%20a%20bit%20of%20training.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bu