loyees-with-rs-1-lakh-esops-on-10th-anniversary-124122300827_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20payments%20fintech%20is%20currently%20in%20the%20process%20of%20reverse%20flipping%20from%20the%20United%20States%20(US)%20to%20India.%20The%20firm%20expects%20to%20complete%20the%20domicile%20shift%20sometime%20in%202025%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BNo%20One%20From%20BJP%20Can...%26quot%3B%3A%20Chhattisgarh%20Chief%20Minister%20On%20Ambedkar%20Row%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20insulted%20BR%20Ambedkar%20in%20his%20lifetime%20and%20is%20in%20no%20position%20to%20point%20fingers%20at%20anyone%2C%20Chhattisgarh%20Chief%20Minister%20Vishnu%20Deo%20Sai%20said%20today%20in%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20row%20over%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah's%20remarks%20about%20the%20architect%20of%20the%20Indian%20constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20matter%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview%2C%20Mr%20Sai%20---%20a%20tribal%20leader%20--%20said%20it%20was%20not%20possible%20that%20anyone%20from%20the%20BJP%20would%20insult%20Ambedkar.%20%26quot%3BWe%20need%20to%20look%20at%20what%20the%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20said%20in%20entirety%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20Mr%20Sai%20said%2C%20has%20shown%20huge%20respect%20to%20Ambedkar%2C%20no%20matter%20who%20headed%20the%20government%20--%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20or%20Narendra%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Congress%20did%20not%20even%20allow%20his%20portrait%20in%20the%20country's%20parliament.%20When%20he%20was%20alive%2C%20they%20insulted%20him%20repeatedly.%20But%20when%20our%20government%20came%20to%20power%2C%20we%20established%20the%20places%20associated%20with%20his%20life%20as%20five%20pilgrim%20centres%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sai%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%20in%20Mau%20where%20he%