o%2Frenault-nissan-s-indian-ties-in-question-amid-honda-nissan-merger-talks-124122301019_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nissan%20Motor%20India%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20matter.%20Honda%20Cars%20India%20too%20did%20not%20comment%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findustry%2Fauto%2Frenault-nissan-s-indian-ties-in-question-amid-honda-nissan-merger-talks-124122301019_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BCreated%20The%20New%20Wave%20Cinema%26quot%3B%3A%20Tributes%20Pour%20In%20For%20Shyam%20Benegal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EVeteran%20filmmaker%20Shyam%20Benegal%2C%20who%20heralded%20the%20Indian%20parallel%20cinema%20movement%20in%20the%201970s%20and%201980s%20with%20films%20such%20as%20'Ankur'%2C%20'Nishant'%20and%20'Manthan'%2C%20died%20at%20a%20Mumbai%20hospital%20on%20Monday%2C%20barely%20a%20week%20after%20celebrating%20his%2090th%20birthday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20filmmaker%20-%20who%20received%20Padma%20Bhushan%20and%20Dadasaheb%20Phalke%20Award%2C%20along%20with%2018%20National%20Film%20Awards%20-%20died%20due%20to%20chronic%20kidney%20disease.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20films%20include%20'Bhumika'%2C%20'Junoon'%2C%20'Mandi'%2C%20'Suraj%20Ka%20Satvaan%20Ghoda'%2C%20'Mammo'%20and%20%26quot%3BSardari%20Begum%26quot%3B%2C%20most%20counted%20as%20classics%20in%20Hindi%20cinema.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20director's%20most%20recent%20work%20was%20the%202023%20biographical%20'Mujib%3A%20The%20Making%20of%20a%20Nation'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20news%20of%20the%20filmmaker's%20death%20spread%2C%20tributes%20poured%20in%20from%20far%20and%20wide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20said%20the%20filmmaker's%20%26quot%3Bstorytelling%20had%20a%20profound%20impact%20on%20Indian%20cinema%26quot%3B.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDeeply%20saddened%20by%20the%20passing%20of%20Shri%20Shyam%20Benegal%20Ji%2C%20whose%20storytelling%20had%20a%20profound%20impact%20on%20Indian%20cinema.%20His%20works%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20admired%20by%20people%20from%20different%20walks%20of%20life.%20Condolences%20to%20his%20family%20and%20admirers.%20Om%20Shanti%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said%20in%20his%20tribute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeader%20of%20Opposition%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20said%20the%20filmmaker%20presented%20%26quot%3BIndia's%20stories%20with%20depth%20and%20sensitivity%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSaddened%20by%20the%20passing%20of%20Shyam%20Benegal%20ji%2C%20a%20visionary%20filmmaker%20who%20brought%20India's%20stories%20to%20life%20with%20depth%20and%20sensitivity.%20His%20legacy%20in%20cinema%20and%20commitment%20to%20social%20issues%20will%20inspire%20generations.%20Heartfelt%20condolences%20to%20his%20loved%20ones%20and%20admirers%20worldwide%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDirector%20Shekhar%20Kapur%20said%20Shyam%20Benegal%20will%20be%20%26quot%3Bremembered%20as%20the%20man%20who%20changed%20the%20direction%20of%20Indian%20cinema%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20created%20'the%20new%20wave'%20cinema.%20%23shyambenegal%20will%20always%20be%20remembered%20as%20the%20man%20that%20changed%20the%20direction%20of%20Indian%20Cinema%20with%20films%20like%20Ankur%2C%20Manthan%20and%20countless%20others.%20He%20created%20stars%20out%20great%20actors%20like%20Shabama%20Azmi%20and%20Smita%20Patil.%20Farewell%20my%20friend%20and%20guide%2C%26quot%3B%20filmmaker%20Shekhar%20Kapur%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20Benegal%20as%20Shyam%20Babu%2C%20as%20he%20was%20known%20to%20friends%20and%20collaborators%2C%20director%20Hansal%20Mehta%2C%20of%20'Shahid'%2C%20'Citylights'%20fame%2C%20thanked%20the%20filmmaker%20for%20being%20an%20inspiration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThank%20you%20for%20the%20cinema.%20Thank%20you%20for%20giving%20tough%20stories%20and%20flawed%20characters%20such%20amazing%20dignity.%20Truly%20among%20the%20last%20of%20our%20greats%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Mehta%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EActor%20Manoj%20Bajpayee%2C%20who%20worked%20with%20Shyam%20Benegal%20in%202001's%20'Zubeidaa'%2C%20said%20the%20director's%20death%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bheartbreaking%20loss%26quot%3B%20for%20Indian%20cinema.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShyam%20Benegal%20wasn't%20just%20a%20legend%2C%20he%20was%20a%20visionary%20who%20redefined%20storytelling%20and%20inspired%20generations.%20Working%20with%20him%20in%20Zubeidaa%20was%20a%20transformative%20experience%20for%20me%2C%20exposing%20me%20to%20his%20unique%20style%20of%20storytelling%20%26amp%3B%20nuanced%20understanding%20of%20performances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'll%20forever%20be%20grateful%20for%20the%20lessons%20I%20learned%20under%20his%20direction.%20It%20was%20an%20absolute%20honor%20to%20have%20had%20the%20opportunity%20to%20work%20with%20him.%20His%20legacy%20will%20live%20on%20in%20the%20stories%20he%20told%20and%20the%20lives%20he%20touched.%20Rest%20in%20peace%20Shyam%20Babu%2C%20Om%20Shanti%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Bajpayee.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFilmmaker%20Sudhir%20Mishra%20said%20Benegal%20was%20the%20best%20at%20expressing%20%26quot%3Bpoetry%20of%20the%20ordinary%20face%20and%20ordinary%20lives%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMuch%20will%20be%20written%20about%20Shyam%20Benegal%20but%20for%20me%20not%20many%20talk%20about%20the%20fact%20that%20there%20was%20a%20lament%20in%20his%20films%20and%20a%20sadness%20about%20the%20fact%20we%20were%20not%20living%20in%20the%20best%20of%20all%20possible%20Worlds%20(sic)%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20another%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFilmmaker%20Sudhir%20Mishra%2C%20who%20spoke%20highly%20about%20the%20director%20when%20he%20launched%20a%20book%20on%20Benegal%20by%20Atul%20Tiwari%20in%20Lucknow%20barely%20three%20days%20ago%2C%20said%20he%20couldn't%20believe%20the%20veteran%20would%20%26quot%3Bleave%20us%20so%20soon%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETelugu%20superstar%20and%20politician%20Chiranjeevi%20also%20paid%20tributes%20to%20Benegal%2C%20a%20fellow%20Hyderabadi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDeeply%20saddened%20at%20the%20departure%20of%20Shri%20Shyam%20Benegal%2C%20one%20of%20the%20finest%20film%20makers%20and%20great%20intellectuals%20of%20our%20country.%20He%20discovered%20%26amp%3B%20nurtured%20some%20of%20the%20brightest%20film%20talents%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHis%20films%2C%20biographies%20and%20documentaries%20form%20part%20of%20India's%20greatest%20cultural%20treasure!!%20A%20fellow%20Hyderabadi%20%26amp%3B%20former%20Rajya%20Sabha%20member%2C%20Benegal%20Sab's%20masterful%20works%20will%20always%20be%20held%20in%20great%20esteem%20in%20Indian%20Cinema!%20Rest%20In%20Peace%20Sir!!%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Chiranjeevi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFarewell%20to%20the%20legendary%20%23ShyamBenegal%2C%20the%20master%20storyteller%20who%20redefined%20Indian%20cinema%20with%20his%20realism%20and%20depth.%20His%20films%20will%20continue%20to%20inspire%20generations.%20Rest%20in%20peace%20maestro%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Bengali%20star%20Prosenjit%20Chatterjee%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734976020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2F9iv8h568_shyam-benegal-_625x300_23_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcreated-the-new-wave-cinema-tributes-pour-in-for-filmmaker-shyam-benegal-7316967%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Veteran%20filmmaker%20Shyam%20Benegal%2C%20who%20heralded%20the%20Indian%20parallel%20cinema%20movement%20in%20the%201970s%20and%201980s%20with%20films%20such%20as%20'Ankur'%2C%20'Nishant'%20and%20'Manthan'%2C%20died%20at%20a%20Mumbai%20hospital%20on%20Monday%2C%20barely%20a%20week%20after%20celebrating%20his%2090th%20birthday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.n