s%2C%20Paid%20For%20Underage%20Sex%2C%20Finds%20Probe%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20former%20US%20lawmaker%20who%20was%20Donald%20Trump's%20first%20pick%20to%20run%20the%20Justice%20Department%20paid%20for%20sex%20numerous%20times%2C%20including%20with%20an%20underage%20girl%2C%20according%20to%20a%20congressional%20report%20released%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMatt%20Gaetz%20also%20regularly%20used%20cocaine%20and%20ecstasy%2C%20and%20bought%20marijuana%20from%20his%20Capitol%20Hill%20office%2C%20according%20to%20the%2037-page%20document%2C%20the%20culmination%20of%20a%20long-running%20probe%20by%20the%20House%20Ethics%20Committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20committee%20determined%20there%20is%20substantial%20evidence%20that%20Representative%20Gaetz%20violated%20House%20rules%20and%20other%20standards%20of%20conduct%20prohibiting%20prostitution%2C%20statutory%20rape%2C%20illicit%20drug%20use%2C%20impermissible%20gifts%2C%20special%20favors%20or%20privileges%2C%20and%20obstruction%20of%20Congress%2C%26quot%3B%20panel%20investigators%20wrote%2C%20according%20to%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGaetz%20has%20repeatedly%20denied%20wrongdoing%20--%20pointing%20to%20the%20Justice%20Department's%20decision%20not%20to%20bring%20charges%20against%20him%20in%202023%20after%20a%20criminal%20probe%20--%20and%20the%20report%20came%20out%20despite%20him%20suing%20the%20committee%20to%20block%20its%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongressional%20investigators%20found%20that%20the%2042-year-old%20broke%20multiple%20Florida%20laws%20on%20sexual%20misconduct%2C%20although%20they%20cleared%20him%20of%20federal%20sex%20trafficking%20violations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20listed%20payments%20by%20Gaetz%20totaling%20more%20than%20%2490%2C000%20to%2012%20women%20%26quot%3Blikely%20in%20connection%20with%20sexual%20activity%20and%2For%20drug%20use%26quot%3B%20between%202017%20and%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20focused%20on%20a%202018%20trip%20to%20the%20Bahamas%20during%20which%20Gaetz%20is%20alleged%20to%20have%20had%20sex%20with%20four%20women%20and%20took%20the%20ecstasy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ex-congressman%20is%20an%20incendiary%20figure%20with%20few%20friends%20on%20Capitol%20Hill%2C%20but%20was%20a%20staunch%20Trump%20loyalist%20and%20a%20favorite%20of%20the%20president-elect's%20ardent%20supporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20resigned%20from%20Congress%20in%20November%20after%20Trump%20nominated%20him%20for%20US%20attorney%20general.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'High%20school'%20victim%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20allegations%20had%20been%20openly%20discussed%20for%20years%20and%20Gaetz%20withdrew%20from%20consideration%20when%20it%20became%20clear%20he%20lacked%20sufficient%20backing%20from%20Republicans%20to%20win%20Senate%20confirmation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGaetz%20posted%20a%20series%20of%20tweets%20refuting%20some%20of%20the%20allegations%20in%20the%20report%2C%20including%20that%20he%20paid%20for%20sex.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGiving%20funds%20to%20someone%20you%20are%20dating%20--%20that%20they%20didn't%20ask%20for%20--%20and%20that%20isn't%20'charged'%20for%20sex%20is%20now%20prostitution%3F!%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20reason%20they%20did%20this%20to%20me%20in%20a%20Christmas%20Eve-Eve%20report%20and%20not%20in%20a%20courtroom%20of%20any%20kind%20where%20I%20could%20present%20evidence%20and%20challenge%20witnesses.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWomen%20told%20congressional%20investigators%20they%20were%20paid%20for%20sex%20at%20parties%20and%20other%20events%20by%20Gaetz%20and%20his%20friend%20Joel%20Greenberg%2C%20a%20former%20tax%20collector%20in%20Florida%20who%20was%20jailed%20for%2011%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20encounter%20allegedly%20involved%20a%2017-year-old%20girl%2C%20who%20told%20the%20committee%20she%20had%20sex%20with%20Gaetz%20twice%20at%20a%20July%202017%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVictim%20A%20r