in%20Delhi%20today%2C%20six%20months%20after%20the%20party%20suffered%20a%20massive%20defeat%20at%20both%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20the%20state%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJD%2C%20which%20has%20been%20ruling%20the%20state%20for%20five%20consecutive%20terms%2C%20won%20only%2051%20of%20the%20state's%20153%20assembly%20constituencies.%20The%20BJP%20won%2078%20and%20in%20a%20first%2C%20came%20to%20power%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20party%20also%20won%2020%20of%20the%20state's%2021%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJD%20has%20now%20given%20a%20memorandum%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%20asking%20about%20the%20discrepancies%20-%20especially%20why%20there%20is%20a%20huge%20gap%20between%20the%20total%20votes%20polled%20in%20a%20booth%20and%20the%20votes%20counted%20from%20the%20EVMs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJD%20has%20also%20pointed%20out%20how%20the%20total%20votes%20polled%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20was%20different%20from%20the%20number%20of%20votes%20cast%20for%20the%20assembly%20segments%20that%20come%20under%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20first%20in%20Odisha%2C%20the%20voting%20percentage%20difference%20between%20polling%20day%20turnout%20and%20the%20final%20turnout%20figure%20is%2015%20per%20cent%20to%2030%20per%20cent.%3Cbr%3E%5CnIn%20Keonjhar%20constituency%2C%20from%20where%20Chief%20Minister%20Mohan%20Charan%20Manjhi%20was%20contesting%2C%20the%20difference%20between%20voting%20percentage%20on%20polling%20day%20and%20the%20final%20percentage%20is%2030.64%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20difference%20is%20the%20highest%20in%20the%20country%20--%20perhaps%20the%20highest%20ever%20in%20the%20country's%20electoral%20history%2C%20the%20party%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20leaders%20claimed%20that%20the%20discrepancy%20is%20high%20enough%20to%20affect%20the%20final%20outcome%20of%20the%20election%20and%20questioned%20how%20this%20could%20happen%20in%20an%20age%20of%20sophisticated%20EVMs%20and%20foolproof%20telecom%20network.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20filed%20an%20application%20with%20the%20Chief%20Election%20Officer%20of%20Odisha%20two%20months%20ago%2C%20asking%20them%20to%20provide%20us%20the%20Form%2017%20data.%20We%20have%20requested%20the%20Commission%20to%20clarify%20the%20discrepancies%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20senior%20party%20leader%20Amar%20Patnaik.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20not%20questioning%20the%20EVM%2C%20we%20are%20questioning%20the%20Election%20process%20in%20which%20the%20EVM%20is%20a%20component%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20the%20Congress%2C%20the%20party%2C%20he%20added%2C%20has%20not%20taken%20any%20call%20on%20the%20ballot%20box.%20%C2%A0%26quot%3BThe%20Election%20Commission%20has%20assured%20us%20that%20it%20would%20look%20into%20the%20matter%20and%20action%20will%20be%20taken%20if%20any%20discrepancies%20are%20found.%20The%20Commission%2C%20however%2C%20has%20not%20given%20any%20timeline%20for%20its%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734971460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fun4s8ug_naveen-patnaik-_625x300_24_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsix-months-after-defeat-in-odisha-bjd-questions-integrity-of-poll-process-7316848%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20the%20Opposition%20parties%20belonging%20to%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20Odisha's%20opposition%20Biju%20Janata%20Dal%20or%20BJD%20has%20red-flagged%20the%20unexplainable%20variances%20in%20the%20voting%20figures%20from%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20state%20assembly%20elections%20held%20earlier%20this%20year.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsix-months-after-defeat-in-odisha-bjd-questions-integrity-of-poll-process-7316848%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22ReNew%20inks%20pact%20with%20Anzen%20to%20sell%20300%20MW%20operational%20solar