ry%20Carro's%2013th-floor%20courtroom%20in%20the%20New%20York%20state%20criminal%20courthouse%20in%20lower%20Manhattan%20with%20a%20court%20officer%20on%20each%20arm%2C%20and%20a%20procession%20of%20a%20half%20dozen%20officers%20following%20him.%20He%20was%20in%20handcuffs%20and%20shackles%2C%20and%20wore%20a%20burgundy%20sweater%20over%20a%20white-collared%20shirt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELuigi%20Mangione%20leaned%20into%20a%20microphone%20and%20said%20%26quot%3Bnot%20guilty%26quot%3B%20when%20Carro%20asked%20how%20he%20pleaded%20to%20the%2011-count%20indictment%20charging%20him%20with%20murder%20as%20an%20act%20of%20terrorism%20and%20weapons%20offenses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20convicted%2C%20he%20faces%20a%20maximum%20sentence%20of%20life%20in%20prison%20without%20the%20possibility%20of%20parole.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThompson%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20UnitedHealth%20Group's%20insurance%20unit%20UnitedHealthcare%2C%20was%20shot%20dead%20on%20Dec.%204%20outside%20a%20hotel%20in%20midtown%20Manhattan%20where%20the%20company%20was%20gathering%20for%20an%20investor%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20brazen%20killing%20and%20ensuing%20five-day%20manhunt%20captivated%20Americans.%20While%20public%20officials%20have%20condemned%20the%20killing%2C%20some%20Americans%20who%20decry%20the%20steep%20costs%20of%20healthcare%20and%20insurance%20companies'%20power%20to%20deny%20paying%20for%20some%20medical%20treatments%20have%20feted%20Mangione%20as%20a%20folk%20hero.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELuigi%20Mangione%20was%20arrested%20at%20a%20McDonald's%20restaurant%20in%20Altoona%2C%20Pennsylvania%2C%20on%20Dec.%209.%20After%20deciding%20last%20week%20not%20to%20fight%20extradition%2C%20he%20was%20transferred%20to%20New%20York%2C%20where%20he%20was%20led%20off%20a%20helicopter%20in%20lower%20Manhattan%20by%20a%20large%20phalanx%20of%20police%20officers%20and%20New%20York%20City%20Mayor%20Eric%20Adams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20spectacle%20and%20other%20statements%20by%20public%20officials%20suggest%20Mangione%20may%20not%20be%20able%20to%20get%20a%20fair%20trial%2C%20his%20lawyer%20Karen%20Friedman%20Agnifilo%20said%20at%20Monday's%20hearing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20are%20treating%20him%20like%20he%20is%20some%20sort%20of%20political%20fodder%2C%20some%20sort%20of%20spectacle%2C%26quot%3B%20Agnifilo%20said.%20%26quot%3BHe%20is%20not%20a%20symbol%2C%20he%20is%20someone%20who%20is%20afforded%20a%20right%20to%20a%20fair%20trial.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20dozen%20people%20gathered%20outside%20the%20courthouse%20in%20freezing%20temperatures%20to%20express%20support%20for%20Mangione%20and%20anger%20at%20healthcare%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20person%20held%20a%20sign%20with%20the%20words%20%26quot%3BDENY%2C%20DEFEND%2C%20DEPOSE%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20phrase%20that%20echoes%20tactics%20some%20accuse%20insurers%20of%20using%20to%20avoid%20paying%20out%20claims.%20Authorities%20say%20the%20words%20%26quot%3Bdeny%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3Bdelay%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bdepose%26quot%3B%20were%20found%20written%20on%20shell%20casings%20at%20the%20crime%20scene.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKara%20Hay%2C%20a%2042-year-old%20schoolteacher%2C%20said%20she%20believed%20it%20was%20wrong%20for%20Mangione%20to%20be%20charged%20with%20terrorism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShooting%20one%20CEO%20does%20not%20make%20him%20a%20terrorist%2C%20and%20I%20do%20not%20feel%20terrorized%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Hay%2C%20who%20held%20a%20sign%20reading%20%26quot%3Binnocent%20until%20proven%20guilty.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%2030-minute%20hearing%2C%20officers%20once%20again%20shackled%20Mangione%20and%20led%20him%20out%20of%20the%20courtroom.%20He%20is%20being%20held%20at%20the%20Metropolitan%20Detention%20Center%2C%20a%20federal%20lockup%20in%20Brooklyn.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECarro%20set%20Mangione's%20next%20court%20appearance%20for%20Feb.%2021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDUAL%20STATE%2C%20FEDERAL%20CASES%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMonday's%20arraignment%20was%20the%20second%20court%20appearance%20in%20New%20York%20for%20Mangione%2C%20who%20also%20faces%20a%20four-count%20federal%20criminal%20complaint%20charging%20him%20with%20stalking%20and%20killing%20Thompson.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20not%20yet%20been%20asked%20to%20enter%20a%20plea%20in%20that%20case.%20U.S.%20Magistrate%20Judge%20Katharine%20Parker%20ordered%20Mangione%20detained%20at%20a%20Dec.%2019%20hearing%20in%20Manhattan%20federal%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20federal%20charges%20would%20make%20him%20eligible%20for%20the%20death%20penalty%2C%20should%20the%20U.S.%20Attorney's%20Office%20in%20Manhattan%20decide%20to%20pursue%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20separate%20federal%20and%20state%20cases%20will%20proceed%20in%20parallel.%20The%20state%20case%20is%20currently%20expected%20to%20go%20to%20trial%20first%2C%20federal%20prosecutors%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20hearing%2C%20Friedman%20Agnifilo%20said%20it%20was%20difficult%20to%20defend%20her%20client%20in%20dual%20state%20and%20federal%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20is%20being%20treated%20like%20a%20human%20ping-pong%20ball%20between%20these%20two%20jurisdictions%2C%26quot%3B%20Friedman%20Agnifilo%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20said%20the%20Manhattan%20District%20Attorney's%20office%2C%20which%20brought%20the%20charges%2C%20has%20not%20handed%20over%20any%20evidence%20to%20the%20defense%20to%20help%20prepare%20for%20trial%2C%20a%20process%20known%20as%20discovery.%20A%20prosecutor%20responded%20that%20the%20office%20would%20begin%20handing%20over%20evidence%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20federal%20criminal%20complaint%2C%20the%20police%20who%20arrested%20Mangione%20found%20a%20notebook%20that%20contained%20several%20handwritten%20pages%20that%20%26quot%3Bexpress%20hostility%20towards%20the%20health%20insurance%20industry%20and%20wealthy%20executives%20in%20particular.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20noteb